34 於永安中心外，示威者呼籲全部人「一齊走」。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D347322312837536&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=47f87a08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:44 警察向示威者開槍。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D336543320631999&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=95084499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999</a><br />\n【721即時】22:38 在示威者推進途中，警方突然向人群射出催淚彈，及急速推進。示威者向警方投擲雜物還擊，警方再發射多枚催淚彈。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D436610810398685&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=d996762e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:12 港澳碼頭外，警察向示威者施放胡椒噴霧。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D497139927720468&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=912040ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:00 干諾道西港澳碼頭外警察突然推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2450364665024731&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=f2384212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731</a><br />\n21:20 警察以「一二一二」的口令由德輔道西向西邊街推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1310939165740421&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=b2bfb7e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421</a><br />\n20:55 中區警署外的示威者向警署外牆掉油漆彈、磚頭及腐蝕性液體 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D725595331211578&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=d4cc44fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578</a><br />\n20:23 有一批全black bloc的警員不斷推進防線，惟沒有委任證及證明文件。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D406909290170265&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=8d789b6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265</a><br />\n20:13 示威者現正由干諾道西向後奔跑至德輔道西。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D789204521474060&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=9305acea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060</a><br />\n <br />\n上環清場中 警方對這個用身體阻擋催淚彈的男人這樣處理 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAzZoteAvCyw&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=491b6ac6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw</a><br />\n示威者疑中槍倒地 同伴築防線助急救 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2433207320290299&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=09f4bfea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299</a><br />\n2019/0721/上環硝煙花特別多 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBpfKm3Ls34U%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=7741c833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n2019/07/21上環。抗爭者心聲。他們有不想活的覺悟。 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DS4OKmzwmhIo&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=e3889e1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo</a><br />\n黑警用橡膠子彈射頭 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F2433207320290299%2F&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=52e04afc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299/</a><br />\n黑警用催淚彈直射向記者 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTeVHAuMLP4&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcTeVHAuMLP4%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=64549850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTeVHAuMLP4&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n[上環 7.21] 蘋果影到有義士訓低咗，綠衫圍著 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ApplePhotographers/photos/a.1131233677080155/1131269430409913?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FApplePhotographers%2Fphotos%2Fa.1131233677080155%2F1131269430409913%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhH0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=33c5176a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ApplePhotographers/photos/a.1131233677080155/1131269430409913?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n（07.21）譴責警察暴力：記者被催淚彈打中，係直接打中！ <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watc